column5: HI ALL  I was looking in my canadaian fly fisher magazine that i receive today.....page 59(nov/jan) edition  and SAW CRAZZYHOOK and is huge carp caught on the fly..   great pict bud......  cong again....   joco
Yup, our boy Jamie has definetely gone over to the dark side   !!
the carpin questio on the pict.  it said on the report in the mag...  carp 25 pound.39inch......8wt rod.6pound tippet...25 min battle.  wow,,,,what a nice carp.on fly.   joco
Yeah, tell us about it Jamie. Was it a corn fly?
He was probably matching the corn hatch  WTG CH
Fly-fishing for Carp?  That must be like Bow-hunting for Chickens...
